title: Utley not in Dodgers' lineup for Game 3 vs Mets
text:
> Sports Utley not in Dodgers' lineup for Game 3 vs Mets Los Angeles Dodgers' Chase Utley, center, listens to the reaction from the crowd as his name is called during pre-game player introductions before baseball's Game 3 of the National League Division Series against the New York Mets, Monday, Oct. 12, 2015, in New York. Pitcher Clayton Kershaw (22) and center fielder Justin Ruggiano looked on. (AP Photo/Julie Jacobson)
